the president of the pagans motorcycle 
club and nine other people pleaded guilty tuesday to drugrelated 
racketeering charges stemming from a multistate federal 
investigation 
daniel dirty dan delp 42 of alliance ohio listed as the 
clubs national president by the us attorneys office entered his 
plea in us district court 
