broiler houses worth 65000 each and 80000 chickens insurance 
will cover most of their losses but not enough for the couple to 
rebuild completely 
my concern with lowinterest loans is that all were doing is 
borrowing money to pay for buildings that are already heavily 
financed mrs thomas said youre paying for them twice 
