magellan space probe to venus 
perched vertically on a giant caterpillartrack transporter the 
shuttle began the fourmile trip at 1201 am reaching the pad 
nearly eight hours later traveling at maximum speed of 1 mph 
at the launch pad atlantis will be prepared for liftoff april 
28 the 7600pound magellan spacecraft will be loaded into the 
shuttles cargo bay friday 
during the first day of the fourday mission the five astronauts 
are to release the probe to begin its 15month outward journey once 
