the universitys behalf for the past seven years seeking jobs for 
graduates and fostering the schools relationship with hokkaido 
university in the city of sapporo 
the japanese university was founded as an agricultural school in 
1876 by william s clark who was third president of the university 
of massachusetts itself founded as an agricultural school 
